description:
The last of the first round matches pits 9th and 10th contenders together. The Assassin "Ariel X" is on a winning streak and she's showing improved skill. She is a trash talker and loves to fuck losers and pound them into the mat.
Athena "Naudia Nyce" is one tough girl; she boxes in her off time and loves the competition. She's also a little crazy, and crazy can bring vasts amount of determination and energy from nowhere.
The winner is moving forward and the loser is going to get a hard punishment fucking.
title: SUMMER VENGEANCE
